Konata Izumi TI

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

Three versions based off of different training methods. The "orig(ingal)" is straight up screenshots from the show, "full" (forgot why I named it this) was reduced size to 512x512 focusing on Konata, and "redux" was a reduction of images from "full" that had parts of other characters.

I personally find the redux version to be best of the three, although it gets confused about the mole. It is supposed to be under the left eye, but tends to end up under the right. If it isn't there, go into ms-paint, choose a black marker, and add it manually.

This does work with clip skip = 1, but no pictures were added below because I think they looks bad. Weights range from .75-1, play with it as needed. Fairly compatible with other TIs and LoRAs, some issue here and there.

For all those interested, all images were taken after the 18th birthday party (episode 17 first 5-ish minutes). Trained on novelai checkpoint at a rate of .0005, all data listed with the original

Токены: konataredux-10000
SHA256: E50F28BA8E3210D362C81BF28C5E7992C7E51C5A74740B7CA6CBB8F448CF7D06

South of the Border Style

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

Follow me to make sure you see new poses and Nobodys when I post them. Things move fast on this site, it's easy to miss.

Embedding to get the Mexican cultural aesthetic to any image quickly and easily. Images were generated using the legendary A to Zovya RPG Artist's Tools V2 model.

Most models have a strong asian style to them, this model does a pretty good job of removing that, but you might find you need to put "asian" in the negative prompt to help it out. Also, anytime models hear mention of Mexico or Mexican, they want to put sombreros on everyone. This model tries to tone that down some but not completely. So prompt "sombrero" or "hat" in the positive or negative prompt as needed.

Do you have requests? I've been putting in many more hours lately with this. That's my problem, not yours. But if you'd like to tip me, buy me a beer. Beer encourages me to ignore work and make AI models instead. Tip and make a request. I'll give it a shot if I can. Here at Ko-Fi

Cobwebber

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

Introduces cobweb into the scene. NOT the typical spiderweb pattern!!
It attaches to objects, can cover objects, possible to create things made out of cobweb.
